Package com.yubico.webauthn.attestation.resolver

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CompositeAttestationResolver
    An AttestationResolver whose CompositeAttestationResolver.resolve(X509Certificate, List) method calls AttestationResolver.resolve(X509Certificate, List) on each of the subordinate AttestationResolvers in turn, and returns the first non-null result.
    CompositeTrustResolver
    A TrustResolver whose CompositeTrustResolver.resolveTrustAnchor(X509Certificate, List) method calls resolveTrustAnchor(X509Certificate, List) on each of the subordinate TrustResolvers in turn, and returns the first non-null result.
    SimpleAttestationResolver  
    SimpleTrustResolver
    Assesses whether an argument certificate can be trusted, and if so, by what trusted root certificate.
